# Testing Standards

- **Rule**: every core feature must have tests.
- **Test pyramid**
  - **Unit**: pure functions (calculations, formatting, template rendering)
  - **Integration**: server handlers + DB (in-memory or test DB)
  - **E2E**: “create invoice → public link → PDF/download → copy follow-up”
- **What is “core” for MVP**
  - invoice totals math
  - public invoice access rules
  - PDF export path (client-side behavior)
  - UPI QR payload generation
  - follow-up template variable substitution
- **Quality gates**
  - No skipped tests for core paths
  - Fix flaky tests immediately
  - Prefer deterministic tests (freeze time, stable IDs)

